      "writtenOn": "2018-08-15T02:50:46Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Investigating further, I don\u0027t think this is required.  Internally we create a buffer that has the correct alignment, so setting it here would actually mismatch.\n\nSimilarly, for the other properties they operate in pixels so we *shouldn\u0027t* override them, they will apply to the decompressed image the same as the compressed one.",
      "parentUuid": "3b4cba43_3bbab338",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 715,
