      "writtenOn": "2018-08-15T03:23:21Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Hmm, yeah you\u0027re right it could potentially read out of bounds in that case.  It seems like the only property that we account for is actually the alignment :-)\n\nIn fact, does glCompressedTexImage2D actually use any of the unpack properties?  The only thing referenced in http://docs.gl/es3/glCompressedTexImage2D is GL_PIXEL_UNPACK_BUFFER_BINDING",
      "parentUuid": "1cb5770b_b2eaeaca",
